investment is made or not (y).
‚Ä¢ A binary Ô¨Åeld for each possible site representing
if that site is open or closed (xjm).
‚Ä¢ A numeric Ô¨Åeld for each contract representing the
assignment between the contracts and service
centers (in place of zijm).
‚Ä¢ A numeric Ô¨Åeld for each level of service engineer
at each possible site (sejlm).

