In this section, we propose two approaches that eliminate feasible solutions that are likely to be inferior without signiÔ¨Åcantly
compromising from optimality. Both approaches utilize the proposed models with some modiÔ¨Åcations. The Ô¨Årst approach is based
on restricting the vehicle to complete at most j1 tours before se
